quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  2,1,Alif Lam Mim
  2,2,"That is Book in which there is no Rayb, guidance for the Muttaqin"
  2,3,"Those Who have faith in the Ghayb and perform Salah, and spend out of what we have provided for them"
  2,4,"And who have faith in what is revealed to you and in what was revealed before you, and in the Hereafter they are certain"
  2,5,"They are on guidance from their Lord, and they are the successful"